{"tid":682482,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[點睇]客機乘客拍到「UFO」在雲層中盤旋","createTime":"2018-05-29T02:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T12:12:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"267d986c54c631af9a4995ef50a795f7114691a6","tid":682482,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:20:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PZmf5RHGPXI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPZmf5RHGPXI&d=Am5SbhvUSQ1Wlx40sPgUt0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4e67797a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PZmf5RHGPXI</a><br />\n<br />\n希臘男子日前搭乘客機出遊時，驚見雲層中有個碟型飛行物體冒出，且不斷翻轉、盤旋飛行。他將視頻上傳網絡後，引起網友熱議，許多網友推測這可能就是UFO吧？<br />\n<br />\n這段視頻是希臘民眾克里&bull;佛萊茲（Kerry Forides）拍攝的，日前他搭機飛越愛琴海時發現不明飛行物體。這個碟狀物先是矗立突出雲層，接著左右擺動後，水平飄出雲層並消失於鏡頭前方。<br />\n<br />\n視頻中可以聽到，佛萊茲的妻子看見這個物體後，驚問「這是什麼東西？」<br />\n<br />\n視頻上傳網絡後，有許多網友直言，佛萊茲用「XDCAM-EX1」攝影機所拍攝到的物體可能就是傳說中的UFO。<br />\n<br />\n不過，也有網友猜測，「這家飛機飛越土耳其戰區，那可能是1枚導彈」、「看起來像是1架戰機的凝結尾」，還有網友認為，「它可能是一種地球工程飛機，在平流層釋放奈米顆粒大小的炭黑粉塵，吸收紫外線以控制氣候」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2018/05/28/859938.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F859938.html&d=Am5SbhvUSQ1Wlx40sPgUt0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=da72b3a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2018/05/28/859938.html</a>"},{"pid":"5059b611b7dc0648eea7f2d091cbff1e4a18ad30","tid":682482,"uid":44333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:22:38.000Z","msg":"我uncle剛從飛機拍到UFO"},{"pid":"bea8b2c0a49a2a12fe68440dde0b2e8e5299b213","tid":682482,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbc9040b45079b65cce89c305d18413f2c866ce","tid":682482,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2250c2a018343e35292503dbc93b523ec233190","tid":682482,"uid":173087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20899ab6d633c33d65b15abdb0faeefd0552143","tid":682482,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"咁薄點坐人? 啲外星人曱甴嚟? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591d07ca39807d430b0391541b49b55f8bac7b80","tid":682482,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"其他乘客既角度呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f625ac3876c7176cf8d0473a6fea9bf4d85872","tid":682482,"uid":45872,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"似凝結尾多喎"},{"pid":"77d7ecf808b62892c27de59851d9339941377123","tid":682482,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:02:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c03c7a206ad5b225cc36b1961fc57bd640f3cb8","tid":682482,"uid":8565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"XDCAM-EX1?<br />\n喺飛機仲有興致隊咁大部野出來影？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b135b69811cebfa8254df14213de4ece9ced02","tid":682482,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:50:01.000Z","msg":"UFO係不明飛行物體<br />\n呢舊野係飛緊，拍果位又唔知佢係咩<br />\n咁叫佢做UFO都好正常呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a69494e70b5b8d3970b59a6d738d9e90b28c908","tid":682482,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,